Youâ€™ll see something like:

â— mediboard.service - Mediboard Fullscreen Launcher
   Loaded: loaded (/etc/systemd/system/mediboard.service; disabled)
   Active: inactive (dead)
âœ… means running
âŒ or â€œinactive (dead)â€ means stopped.

ğŸ§¹ 4. (Optional) Remove the Service Completely
If you no longer want it at all:

